title: Bobbi Brown VS TikTok Beauty Community… our thoughts
description:
Happy FOOL Friday! This week on Fool Coverage Manny and Laura cover the latest details of the Amber and Johnny case, tell the tea of what happened on the Benefit trip starting with an American Airlines horror story, Bobbi Brown vs Meredith foundation feud, Laura and Tyler's anniversary, Manny's villian era on TikTok, and much more!
Follow Laura on IG: @larlarlee
Follow Manny on IG: @mannymua733
